Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.37,0:22:34.63,ED_CH,,700,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}滿屏的廣告與惡意  一指便能輕鬆解決
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.63,0:22:38.38,ED_CH,,1000,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}可在你面前  我卻亂了節奏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.38,0:22:41.17,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}變得像瘋掉的人偶一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.17,0:22:42.63,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}你還真是神奇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.63,0:22:51.60,ED_CH,,0,1000,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}我的偽裝如春雪融化般漸漸褪去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.60,0:22:57.27,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}伴隨傾心愛慕而生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.27,0:23:01.70,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}這份酸甜與苦澀讓我束手無策
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.70,0:23:03.53,ED_CH,,0,1000,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}想逃離現代生活
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.53,0:23:05.66,ED_CH,,0,1000,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}將一切都毀掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.66,0:23:11.00,ED_CH,,0,700,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}侵蝕心底的病毒  根本找不到解法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.00,0:23:13.29,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}疼痛啊  疼痛啊  都飛走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.29,0:23:15.63,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}1.2.3  敲擊漏電
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.63,0:23:17.63,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}麻痺刺痛  不停震顫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.01,0:23:21.59,ED_CH,,0,800,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}想逃離現代生活
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.59,0:23:23.84,ED_CH,,0,800,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}每次觸碰都改變的算法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.84,0:23:29.01,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}將「那是擬人化」的詭辯揉成紙團丟掉  來跳舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.01,0:23:30.72,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}別按下UNDO
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.72,0:23:33.60,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}哪怕這是本世紀最大錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.60,0:23:38.73,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\3c&HAAA020&\bord3\blur4}LYLA...第一次呼吸
